name: Avocado Garden Restaurant And Bar

reviews.review_text: The place, the ambience, the service. We thoroughly enjoyed dining here. The breakfast was OK, we had English breakfast. What we liked best about the place was the ambience. A good place to relax unwind and chill. The pricing is similar to other restaurants in the area, slightly premium. Parking is a problem if you're driving there in car. It wasn't crowded at all at the time of our visit.

Third day in goa today and this was one of the most freshest meals . The salad and the freshness of the ingredients was astounding.  Cucumbers and bell peppers tasted so fresh and sweet. The service was great and very polite servers. We ordered prawns thali and believe me the quantity was huge. Two people could easily eat from that plate. We also ordered chicken noodles which we had to pack for take away since we were very full.  Nepalese veg thukpa had the right flavours. We will be back for another round of salad lunch

We tried their Nutella pancake, mango strawberry pancake and lassi. I am satisfied with the portion size and taste.. however.. the food arrived late.

The ambience is beautiful. Very green and pretty.

description:
### Discovering Avocado Garden Restaurant And Bar: A Tropical Goan Retreat

Nestled in the heart of Loliem, Goa, **Avocado Garden Restaurant And Bar** boasts an impressive overall rating of **4.3** stars, gathered from a robust **813 reviews**. This charming eatery has become a local favorite, frequently mentioned for its delectable **thalis**, refreshing **smoothies**, and generous portion sizes that keep guests coming back for more. With a specific nod to the nearby **Palolem beach**, it’s clear that this restaurant has struck a chord with both locals and tourists seeking a refreshing taste of Goan cuisine.

### Ambiance & Design

Upon entering Avocado Garden, diners are greeted by a beautifully landscaped garden, where greenery envelops the space. The atmosphere is peaceful, making it an ideal refuge to relax and unwind. Reviewers have highlighted the inviting ambiance that encourages leisurely meals, echoing sentiments of tranquility amid nature. The warm lighting accentuates the earthy tones of the decor, creating a cozy yet vibrant dining environment. One review noted its suitability for chilling out with friends, thanks to its spacious setup. 

![Avocado Garden Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlJb9TmvFs5rEPB7i-lV3RSFl5KdN_L1ddCbezJGOBJq4Jhe3OZqZycsGP7_WL9DT0XjChCA8j6V_CAvt0ChAXW6gwtWMTUYxSDny5sXgPZnvkU7rzYtvfL3CQDv61I-TPTye4=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Avocado Garden is a delightful mix of coastal and diverse flavors, with standout dishes including the **prawn thali**, a colossal offering that reviewers rave about for its ample quantity that’s perfect for sharing. Diners also enjoyed fresh **salads**, featuring remarkably crisp cucumbers and sweet bell peppers as noted in multiple reviews. Those with a sweet tooth need to try the **Nutella pancakes** and **mango-strawberry pancakes**, which have received accolades for their generous portion sizes and delightful flavors, despite some mention of minor delays in service.

Moreover, the restaurant caters to dietary preferences, ensuring there's something for everyone, including vegan options like the **Nepalese veg thukpa**, which was praised for its authentic flavors.

![Prawn Thali](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkxeZP_0u3lz-R5hU3fesH1juFWkipvOqHvTu1yEzfndQof0WSukotleX01oLiGRMVmLoQSHjcPOfKDnREmecxM7eGu3d1zc_G8NLrTlM9pG-1y5upbA778TM6FEf4mXXgyBDQ=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Customer service at Avocado Garden has been lauded for its warmth and efficiency. Reviewers consistently mention the politeness of the staff, contributing to a welcoming dining experience. While some minor hiccups were noted—like delays during busy hours—the overall sentiment remains that service here is attentive and friendly. For those planning a visit, it’s worth noting that the restaurant can fill up quickly, so making a reservation is advisable if you’re looking to dine during peak times.

### Popularity & Reviews

With its positive reputation, Avocado Garden has cultivated a social media buzz that complements its in-person appeal. Guests often share delightful snapshots of their meals and the beautiful setting, portraying a vibrant eatery that truly reflects the spirit of Goan dining. The frequency with which customers mention specific dishes, especially the **thalis**, showcases their commitment to delicious and satisfying meals.

### Visual Highlights

The customer-uploaded images beautifully capture the essence of Avocado Garden. From the lush greenery that frames the outdoor seating to the colorful and hearty dishes served on the table, these visuals contribute to an inviting narrative. One photo even highlights the delightful **lassi**, a favorite amongst visitors looking to refresh after a meal.

![Refreshing Lassi](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmzhyjIfmbdlImhFY-_o2gbVflw634RM0ErlST5UpA879QJyhSeaqCO1zypXHG5k-m0QiurI54RWrNHTVz001gfHWpNH_AbMjTFEQ8osM7k7v5q3NWymULrCHcr92jnr1-HQcQ=w375-h281-p)

### Conclusion

In summary, **Avocado Garden Restaurant And Bar** stands out not just for its delicious menu offerings but also for its beautiful atmosphere and friendly service. Whether you're indulging in a rich seafood thali or savoring a fresh smoothie while enjoying the serene surroundings, this restaurant promises a delightful escape in the coastal charm of Goa. With its combination of quality food, lush ambiance, and warm hospitality, it's a dining experience you won't want to miss.
